{"tid":505352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"青山道七旬婦遭吊臂貨車撞斃 親友認屍痛哭","createTime":"2017-12-21T04:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T09:25:53.000Z","uid":126766,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8cd4470050b7c3c45d260e3ceb1b07a2feef1d","tid":505352,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:34:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1093664/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.uk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1093664%2F&d=pLN3bEDIYDO9G7KjYHSZGzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=93217d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.co.uk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1093664/</a><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣發生車禍！一名七旬老婦疑遭吊臂貨車撞倒，頭部受重創當場死亡。警方正調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n事發在下午約1時54分，一名年約70歲的女子於青山道近光昌街橫過馬路時，疑遭一輛駛至的吊臂貨車撞倒，她頭部受重傷，昏迷倒臥地上。途人見狀協助報警，救護員趕至經檢驗後，證實老婦當場死亡。警方封鎖現場調查，並以帳篷遮蓋死者遺體。至於涉事司機則在現場接受警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n死者的2男1女親友事後趕至現場認屍，其中一人痛哭流淚。據悉，警方初步不排除老婦頭部曾被吊臂貨車輾過。<br />\n<br />\n香港地興幸有呢d司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又少一件亂過馬路既廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b183d6d6f98efad118139a78097dd204a3f51cf3","tid":505352,"uid":53568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"我年紀做得佢地老母 無理由唔讓我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a8b236b44b9a21956d2c6f00448df75d20335a","tid":505352,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"非黑心，無啦啦死左好幸福"},{"pid":"9a4f49fdc7d626dbfc1a99b863b7f47a30ed8b4b","tid":505352,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"有無拎埋冠軍金牌上路"},{"pid":"49f71c01baecf576c91962d3a3cc23178ff54034","tid":505352,"uid":46373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"害左個司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d82966a3c2a125a764d4b400a19adfd0036434","tid":505352,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"認真 咁司機計唔計犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}